Noether Forge is a live reviewer environment.

The wj session is trusted as the local live console and may use narrowly
command-restricted doas without a password. wj_low has no administrative authority.

The loaded nftables policy is default-drop with loopback-only allowances.
That policy is not a claim of general runtime sandboxing or OS containment.

